hopobject.body: What sort of music do you listen to? does promethazine relieve nausea vomiting Today, however, I feel that something big may be stirring in Somerset: although it can’t boast a museum equivalent of Tate St Ives or Pallant House, history-book celebrities or epic landscapes, its rough-edged, low-cost charms have attracted the migration of a stream of younger artists and makers – eddying in particular round the pleasant urban environments of Bruton, Frome and Castle Cary, where they contribute considerably to the local economy and quality of life.
